      </div>
    </div>
            <div class="collapse" id="education">
              <div class="card card-body ">
                <h5>Wake Tech Community College   -<small class="mb-1 font-weight-light"> Associates in Web Development </small></h5>

                <div> I had a very good experience at Wake Tech. I learn a lot, but not limited to conceptual programming, design principles, JavaScript, PHP, database concepts, web analytic, and SEO integration. The teachers were very knowledgable and the school provided a lot of resources for our success. They provided everyday personal tutor as well as online help in the form of Lynda.com </div>

                <hr>
                <h5>Code Immersion   -<small class="mb-1 font-weight-light"> Tech Talent South (2 months)</small></h5>

                <div> TTS is one of the top 5 boot camp in the Southern States and was rated the top 50 boot camp in America by CourseReport. I took the 2 month Code Immersion course which taught Full Stack development. This skills and tools I learned are HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, Ruby, Ruby on Rails, Javascript, and Version Control. </div>

                <hr>
                <h5>Javascript Application Development   -<small class="mb-1 font-weight-light"> Tech Talent South (3 months)</small></h5>

