                <hr>
                <h5>Next Level Rails -<small class="mb-1 font-weight-light"> Tech Talent South (1 month)</small></h5>

                <div> Wanting to better my Ruby on Rails skills I decided to take the leap and took the advance ROR course offered by TTS. Next Level Rails taught me Test Driven Development, automated testing, and building my own API.</div>                
             </div>
            </div>

            <div class="collapse" id="skill">
              <div class="card card-body about-card-bg">
                <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
                  <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                      <h5 class="lead"><%= skill.title %></h5>              
                    </div><!--end of first col-->
                    <div class="col-md-8">
                      <div class="progress">
                        <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated" role="progressbar"
                        aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%">
                        </div>
                      </div>
                   </div>                     
                  </div><!--end of row-->   
                <% end %>

  </div>
</div><!-- end of container-->
